{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_12_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 本当の始まり",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃、結成した時の葵は今よりも自由気ままで\nよく私と衝突していたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ when we first formed the group‚ Aoi was even more free-spirited than she is now.\nWe clashed with each other all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせをすっぽかして勝手に練習していたり、好み\nじゃない振り付けや衣装に、いろいろと文句を言ったり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’d skip meetings to practice on her own‚\nand complain about choreography or outfits she didn’t like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5415195782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、パフォーマンスは完璧だったけれど\n私もその時は今よりその……尖っていたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ her performances themselves were flawless.\nAnd back then I was more… prickly than I am now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "つい葵を厳しく指導し過ぎてしまって……\n私達の関係は、デビュー早々ぎくしゃくしていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I ended up being too strict with her…\nOur relationship was awkward right from the start of our debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8603406269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか？　リズノワのステージは\nデビュー当時からずっと息がピッタリじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? LizNoir’s stage performances\nhave looked perfectly in sync ever since your debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4964402516
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ダンスに関してはね\nでも、ステージを降りた途端、またすぐに喧嘩よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ at least when it came to dancing.\nBut the moment we stepped off stage‚ we’d start arguing again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4360996247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "見えないところで、そんなことになっていたとは\n……全然気付きませんでしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think things were like that behind the scenes…\nI had no idea at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6391159374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "葵も私も、まだ互いを理解出来ていなかったのかもね\nそんな中私達の初のワンマンライブが決まったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe neither Aoi nor I really understood each other yet.\nAnd in the middle of all that‚ our first solo live was decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2521086057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1957824706
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1957824706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "お願いよ、葵。我がままばかり言わないでちょうだい\n「こんなひらひらした衣装、着たくない」なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ Aoi. Stop being so stubborn.\nSaying things like “I don’t want to wear such a frilly outfit”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7521086057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.0725396473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の言う通り、少し踊りにくいかもしれないけど\n今から衣装を作り直すなんて出来ないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like you said‚ it might be a little hard to dance in‚\nbut we can’t remake the costumes now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0854419391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2436733245
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2436733245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、怒らなかったんですね。俺の名刺を捨てた\n莉央さんならもっとキツいことを言いそうですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh‚ you didn’t get angry. I thought you’d say something much harsher‚\nlike when you threw away my business card‚ Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.9280960718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼ね！\n私の方が葵よりずっと大人なのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-how rude!\nI’m far more mature than Aoi‚ you know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9365303357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.3147629101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "葵の気持ちを分かってあげなきゃいけない、と思って\nちゃんと優しくさとしたに決まってるじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I had to understand how she felt‚\nso of course I tried to reason with her gently!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、葵は納得出来なかったみたいで……\n何も言わずに、その場を飛び出してしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But it seems Aoi wasn’t convinced…\nShe ran out without saying a word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5031970024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5696.8029976000025,
          "startTime": 118.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.1382320403
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.1382320403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "それから、当時まだバンプロに在籍していた三枝さんと\n私とで、慌てて葵を探し回ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ Saegusa-san—who was still at Van pro at the time—\nand I hurriedly searched everywhere for Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.9261457443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "葵、どこにいるのー！？　葵ー！\nどうしよう、私がムキになり過ぎたせいだわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ where are you―!? Aoi―!\nWhat should I do… This is my fault for getting too heated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.9048068047
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.9048068047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "当時、葵はまだ小学生ですから、心配だったでしょう\nそれで……葵は見つかったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then Aoi was still in elementary school‚ so you must have been worried.\nSo… did you find Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ……葵の行きそうな場所は全部探したんだけど\n見つけられなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… We searched everywhere she might go‚\nbut we couldn’t find her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3632195155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.2648214023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "今考えたら、公園で踊ってるって\n分かるけれど、当時はまだ知らなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about it now‚ she was probably dancing in a park‚\nbut we didn’t know that back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0632103602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.800624911
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.800624911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央。後は俺が探しておくから今日はもう家に帰って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio. I’ll keep looking‚ so go home for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8006355921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "休んだ方がいい。そんなに深刻に考えるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should get some rest. Don’t think about it so seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7965436935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 169.1688664436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん……でも……！\n……分かりました。ご迷惑掛けて、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san… but…!\n…Alright. I’m sorry for causing trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.1965436935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.4295243898
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.4295243898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "私も大人だし、葵にばかり構っていられないから\n一人で家に帰ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m an adult too—I can’t keep focusing only on Aoi.\nSo I went home alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.6298770268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時よ。私の部屋のインターホンが鳴ったのは\n部屋の前に立っていたのは……葵だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then… the intercom to my room rang.\nThe one standing in front of my door… was Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.1298770268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.3973908105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "葵がドアを開けた瞬間のことは、今でも覚えてるわ\nその時の葵ったら、どんな表情してたと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still remember the moment I opened the door.\nWhat kind of face do you think Aoi had?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.6965345382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "息を切らせて、泣きそうな顔をしてて……\nあんなに必死な葵、今になるまで見たことがないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was out of breath and looked like she was about to cry…\nI’ve never seen her that desperate before or since.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.2298729578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.9222936629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "葵ったら、私に直接謝るために\n三枝さんから私の住所まで聞いたらしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ Aoi even asked Saegusa for my address\nso she could apologize to me in person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.8632062911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも早く私に謝りたいからって、急いでうちまで\n来たのよね。……ふふっ、可愛いかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She hurried all the way to my place just to apologize\nas soon as possible. …Fufu‚ it was adorable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.2965396244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.8640848794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに素直な葵、俺には全然想像出来ませんよ\n葵が自分でそう言ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t imagine Aoi being that straightforward at all.\nDid Aoi tell you that herself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 238.5115001995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "あら。あの顔を見たら、言われなくても分かるわよ\nだから、私が大人になってあげたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? I could tell just by looking at her face.\nSo I decided to be the mature one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.3106216113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さん、さっきからやけに大人を強調するな……）\n（でも、多分触れない方がいいんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rio-san keeps emphasizing how “mature” she was…）\n（But I probably shouldn’t point that out.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 255.1617947579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "それに、葵が何か言い出す前にね……ふふっ\nあの子のお腹が大きな音を立てたのよ。ぐぅ～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And before Aoi could say anything… fufu.\nHer stomach growled loudly—like grrrr~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.3516871453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "だから、汗だくのあの子をお風呂に突っ込んで\nその間に、腕によりをかけてパンケーキを焼いたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I made that sweaty girl go take a bath‚\nand while she was bathing‚ I put extra effort into making pancakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.5516871453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 272.7218015672
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
