      "text": "それから二人でパンケーキを食べたわ\n……あの時のパンケーキの味は、いまだに覚えてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then the two of us ate them together.\n…I still remember how those pancakes tasted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.2850204786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、凄く美味しかったでしょう\nそれで二人は、本当に仲直り出来たんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They must have been really delicious.\nAnd that’s how you two truly made up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 286.7904867491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、食べながら、いろんなことを話し合ったわ\n二人の価値観の違いとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. While eating‚ we talked about many things.\nOur differences in values‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.745882384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "今度のワンマンライブでやりたいこととか\nこれからのリズノワのやり方とか……夜遅くまでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "what we wanted to do at the upcoming solo live‚\nand how LizNoir should move forward… late into the night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.345882384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 301.9745005926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、リズノワ初のワンマンライブの結果は\n……聞くまでもありませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then the result of LizNoir’s first solo live was—\n…I guess I don’t even need to ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大成功よ。私は私で、葵の意見を汲んで\n衣装や振り付けを調整してもらったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it was a huge success. I took Aoi’s opinions into account\nand had the costumes and choreography adjusted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.3392158508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 317.2690133413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio030.m4a",
      "text": "葵も、元々の衣装や振り付けの意図を汲んでくれた\nおかげで、本番のパフォーマンスは最高だったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Aoi respected the original intentions behind them as well.\nThanks to that‚ our performance on the day was incredible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.0058825175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio031.m4a",
      "text": "……あの日が、私達二人の関係の\n本当の始まりだったのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That day might have been the true beginning\nof the relationship between the two of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
